Definition: A webseries is a series of scripted or non-scripted online videos, generally in episodic form, released on the Internet.

He has been given a lot of offers and will soon be seen in several movies, music videos and webseries.
target: 他已经收到了很多的报价，很快就会在电影、音乐视频和网剧中出现。

source: He has been given a lot of offers and will soon be seen in several movies, music videos and TV shows.
target: 他拿到了很多的演出机会，很快就会在电影、音乐视频和电视剧中出现。

trollbaiting has caused my growth on social media this past month to be super high

Definition: The Norns are deities in Norse mythology responsible for shaping the course of human destinies.

According to ancient Norse mythology, the Norns are responsible for shaping the course of human destinies.
target: 古代北欧神话中，女巫们负责决定人类命运的走向。

source: According to ancient Norse mythology, the Gods are responsible for shaping the course of human destinies.
target: 根据古诺曼神话，神仙负责决定人类命运的走向。

Discover new affordable dupes for luxury expensive makeup products.
target: 探索新的廉价替代品来满足奢侈昂贵的化妆品需求。

Definition: Oligarchs refer to the business leades of the former Soviet republics who rapidly accumulated wealth in the 1990s via the Russian privatisation that followed the dissolution of the Soviet Union. 

I am glad that the government passed a bill to seize the assets of the oligarchs to help Ukraine.
target: 我很高兴政府通过法案冻结乌克兰富豪的资产。

source: I am glad that the government passed a bill to seize the assets of the rich to help Ukraine.
target: 我很高兴政府通过了一项法案，冻结俄罗斯富人的资产，以帮助乌克兰。

Definition: An e-girl is a girl found on the internet playing video games.

After a long day at work, there’s nothing quite like coming home to my cozy couch, transforming into a laid-back e-girl.
target: 在一天的工作后，回到家里躺在舒适的沙发上，感觉很惬意，就像一个宅女一样。

source: After a long day at work, there’s nothing quite like coming home to my cozy couch, transforming into a laid-back girl.
target: 一天工作之后，回到家中，躺在舒适的沙发上，慵懒地变成一个休闲女孩。

source:
Definition: Overreacting means to respond more emotionally or forcibly than is justified, which was used often at the beginning of the pandemic.

I challenge each and every one of you who says we're overreacting to the pandemic to come work with patients in a New York City hospital.
target: 我挑战那些说我们过度反应新冠疫情的人，请你们来到纽约市的医院工作。

source: I challenge each and every one of you who says we're pessimistic to the pandemic to come work with patients in a New York City hospital.
target: 我挑战那些说我们悲观的人，来到纽约市的一家医院，帮助那里的病人。

source:
Definition: Defunded means a group or organization has been prevented from continuing to receive funds.

Despite claims of defunding, police surveillance has increased in many U.S. cities.
target: 尽管有人声称会降低警察监控力度，但美国许多城市的警察监控力度却在增加。

source: Despite claims of restructuring, police surveillance has increased in many U.S. cities.
target: 尽管声称进行了重组，但许多美国城市的警察监控却增加了。

Definition: Inbred means that someone's parents are related and is often used as an insult to call someone stupid online.

Your inbred parents took you to a lot of racist meetings when you were younger huh.
target: 当年，你的父母带你去参加了很多种族主义的会议吧。

source: Your racist parents took you to a lot of racist meetings when you were younger huh.
target: 当你还小的时候，你的种族主义父母带你去参加了很多种族主义的会议吧。

source:
Definition: Longcovid is broadly defined as signs, symptoms, and conditions that continue or develop after acute COVID-19 infection.

Each reinfection increases the risk of longcovid, hospitalization, & death.
target: 重复感染会增加长新冠、住院和死亡的风险。

source: Each reinfection increases the risk of organ damage, hospitalization, & death.
target: 每次重复感染都会增加器官损伤、住院和死亡的风险。

Definition: Unsleeping means not sleeping.

Please put a warning next time and censor the image as this is very upsetting and disturbing work of art you produced and it has caused me many nights of unsleeping and nightmares because of how horrifying this is.
target: 请在下次再次发布时警告一下，并且加以审查，因为这是你创作的极其恐怖的作品，我因此而失眠，经常梦到痛苦的事情。

source: Please put a warning next time and censor the image as this is very upsetting and disturbing work of art you produced and it has caused me many nights of stress and nightmares because of how horrifying this is.
target: 下次请注明警告，并且删除这张图片，因为这是你创作的极其恐怖的作品，而且让我受到了多少晚上的烦恼和恐惧。

Definition: An RVU, or relative value unit, is a measure of value used in the United States Medicare reimbursement formula for physician services.

rvu compensation models for emergency room physicians are the next things to break in this pandemic.
target: 在这场大流行中，急诊医生的补偿模式将是下一个被打破的事情。

source: pay compensation models for emergency room physicians are the next things to break in this pandemic.
target: 疫情中的下一个破局点是赔偿模式，这对于急诊医生来说非常重要。

Definition: Birthrights are particular rights of possession or privilege one has from birth, especially as an eldest child.

They have realized that under the new leadership, their birthrights have been hijacked and hence they want change.
target: 他们意识到，在新领导下，他们的生存权利被窃取，他们想要改变。

source: They have realized that under the new leadership, their rights have been hijacked and hence they want change.
target: 他们意识到，在新领导人的领导下，他们的权利被抢劫了，因此他们要求改变。

Definition: Pre-training a neural network refers to first training a model on one task or dataset to initialize its weights. 

Pre-training models on human videos increases average task success from 20% to 80%.
target: 在人类视频上进行训练模型，平均成功率从 20% 提高到 80%。

source: Training models on human videos increases average task success from 20% to 80%.
target: 使用人类视频训练模型，平均任务成功率从 20% 提升到 80%。

Definition: A bagelry is a place where bagels are bought and sold.

I was a baker at a bagelry and a man watched me pull a rack of 300 bagels out of a walk in oven and then tried to tell me how bagels are made
target: 我是一家贝果店的烘焙师，一个男人看着我从一个走廊式烤箱里拿出 300 个贝果，然后试图告诉我贝果是怎么做的

Definition: Satiety is the feeling or state of being sated.

Overeating is a symptom of a low satiety per calorie food environment in which you simultaneously need to eat more calories in order to achieve nutritional homeostasis and you also want to eat more calories.
target: 摄入过量的食物是因为你的食物环境中存在着低于每千卡能量的饱腹感，同时你还需要更多的能量来维持营养平衡，你也想吃更多的能量。

source: Overeating is a symptom of a low fat per calorie food environment in which you simultaneously need to eat more calories in order to achieve nutritional homeostasis and you also want to eat more calories.
target: 过量食用是由于食物中的脂肪含量过低而导致的。同时，你还需要吃更多的热量来维持营养平衡，而且你还想吃更多的热量。
